{"tid":1194433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大數據系統顯示「反送中」遊行人數逾 75 萬人","createTime":"2019-06-09T09:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T09:56:29.000Z","uid":11148,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b0566eb952ce0f439093f69b7efeeea99be9f087","tid":1194433,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T09:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/l_HRZGm_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fl_HRZGm_1200x0.png&h=de2cf086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關於 6 月 9 日的「反送中」大遊行有多少人參與，事前沒有任何機構作出預估，民陣或一些召集人的目標設定 30 萬人。為此我嘗試以專門以大數據追蹤趨勢移動 TMA（Trending Moving Average）系統進行演算。<br />\n<br />\n系統對比了 2013 年至 2019 年的 6 年數據，顯示這次「反送中」遊行人數有機會超逾 75.5 萬人次，幾乎肯定超過 2014 年 71 大遊行時的 51 萬人。<br />\n<br />\n據民陣在 2014 年估計，當年 71 參與遊行的人數達到時 51 萬人，以港大民意研究計劃及警方的的估算則分別達到 17.2 萬人及高峰期 9.86 萬人。TMA 系統估算當日遊行人數介乎 40 萬至 53 萬人。值得留意的是，系統顯示今次「反送中」遊行的人數遠高於 2014 年 7 月 1 日，介乎 48.7 萬至 75.49 萬人，成為近 15 年以來最多人上街的一次。<br />\n<br />\nTMA 系統對比了遊行前一天以「遊行」作為關鍵詞在 Google 搜尋的數據，再進行交叉對比及調整，得出介乎 48.7 萬至 75.49 萬人的數據。<br />\n<br />\n對於遊行或創下 15 年以來新高，我不感欣慰，事關遊行人數多少與政府是否聽從民意沒有直接關係，最大機會是「意見接納態度依舊」，相反激進組織或挾這 75 萬人次的遊行而提出激烈訴求，包括重演 2014 年 7 月 1 日後的佔中行動，上演「佔中 2.0」。<br />\n<br />\n目前多個激進組織呼籲支持者在遊行後不要解散，以「不散」作為口號，並強調有重要事情宣布，以過激行動挾遊行以令政府，騎劫遊行，最終釀成流血衝突，這才是我最憂慮的事情，還請各方三思，而遊行人士請注意個人安全，以免遊行和平訴求的目的被盜。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E9%80%BE-75-%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%25B8%25E9%2580%25BE-75-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&d=QsQvn9KnS4zrnMXWGBKJeJ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=1936ad0c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2595%25B8%25E9%2580%25BE-75-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F&h=9f76d75b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E9%80%BE-75-%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA/</a><br />\n75 萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444a60152642ef469c6b2b599641678234f365da","tid":1194433,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T09:26:01.000Z","msg":"用搜尋人數黎計都得？"},{"pid":"67dcdc70bf073ab1c75ab96499ccd3ee875651c4","tid":1194433,"uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T09:26:47.000Z","msg":"黑警+雷教授：2萬"},{"pid":"5d335e423aa3162179000091e20c8b246bf9584a","tid":1194433,"uid":54337,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"67dcdc70bf073ab1c75ab96499ccd3ee875651c4","tid":1194433,"uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T09:26:47.000Z","msg":"黑警+雷教授：2萬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T09:27:17.000Z","msg":"信得2萬嘅都戇鳩"},{"pid":"8675a26f51a9d19ac44fd1d2bc5e9dd54f049a75","tid":1194433,"uid":237024,"like":0,"dislike":32,"score":-32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T09:27:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c32b42eaf2578d93957652870a6e5245025821da","tid":1194433,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T09:28:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8aefbd3bb6702617035